			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Dear Ramesh,</p>
<p>I have seen these ads too and the constant joke in my family is let us call Pandit Maharaj to solve so and so problem.  It is just amazing how much money these people must be making to put up so many ads on ZeeTV. </p>
<p>But, the thing is, when my child was very sick, at some point, I was one phone call away from calling Pandit Maharaj to get some help. Desperate situations require desperate measures!  Even if there was 1% chance that he could help, I was willing to spend whatever it takes. However, by God&#8217;s grace the situation resolved and I (thankfully) did not have to make the call! </p>
<p>Take care and good luck with the course on entrepreneurism. Any possibility of offering it online?</p>
<p>Anon</p>
<p>ps: Writing as anonymous so that I dont have to reveal &#8220;..  educated and highest paid..&#8221; person who thought about asking for Baba&#8217;s help!!</p>
